snippet.title: The Last Sky Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description: The Last Sky is a contemplative puzzle adventure dealing with existential themes of life, guilt, and hope. Solve mind-bending puzzles, flow through mysterious environments, and choose your own adventure as you lead Jake on the path of redemption through a beautiful dreamlike world.
